author: lathomas
body:
Very basic PR to add  HLT_Mu17_TrkIsoVVL_Mu8_TrkIsoVVL_DZ_Mass3p8 to the list of paths monitored by the TOP DQM monitoring tools. 
The two files are copied from https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/19119  and I simply added an extra line for HLT_Mu17_TrkIsoVVL_Mu8_TrkIsoVVL_DZ_Mass3p8 

Hope it's all right... 

Let me know if this is the right way to proceed and I'll make the same for 93X. 
Thanks, 

Laurent
title: Adding HLT_Mu17_TrkIsoVVL_Mu8_TrkIsoVVL_DZ_Mass3p8 to offline DQM
